# ENTSO-E Transparency Platform API token.
# 1. Register: https://transparency.entsoe.eu/  (free account)
# 2. Email transparency@entsoe.eu from your registered address, subject
#    "Restful API access", asking for API access. They reply within ~3 business days.
# 3. Once granted: My Account Settings -> "Web Api Security Token" -> Generate.
# Then copy this file to .env and paste the token below.
ENTSOE_API_TOKEN=your_token_here
